<plot>Rosella Wu is convinced by her mother to kill her mobster husband Danny. But when Danny quits the mob and cleans up his act, she tries to cancel the hit. Except she's too late - the hit man crashes into the house, guns blazing. Now Rosella must stop the hit man, prevent Danny from finding out it was her, and stand up to her over-bearing mother who still wants Danny dead.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?561218</url></doc>
